This is simple project which creates one process which accept one directory name. 
That process will rename all names of regular files with sequential number. (1.txt, 2.txt, 3.txt, 4.txt etc).
This project use make commands to build and execute.Use <make> or <make build> commad to build the project.Use <make help> for help and more details about how to give commands and execute the project. 
